snippet.textDisplay:
Getting emotional on a song
If I ever tell it to somebody, they'll laugh at me even at the thought of it because the side of me they are familiar with is cold and aloof
The song regardless of the reason behind it. It just touched something in deepest part of our hearts.
Everybody have problem and hardships in their life but listening to this song keeps all of us from falling apart.
It's keeps us steady and to fight for ourselves and our beloved family.
I have tears in my eyes how can a  human being write such divine feeling lines and music.
I am in awe and emotional at the fact that I am so lucky to be born in a country ,in a culture where I can understand such deep thoughts. 
Just wanted to say this.
